            <fr:title text="Weeknotes 2025-W16 › Speaking at YaMCaTS 37 next week"><fr:link href="/2025-W16/" title="Weeknotes 2025-W16" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/2025-W16/" display-uri="2025-W16" type="local">Weeknotes 2025-W16</fr:link> › Speaking at <fr:link href="/yamcats-37/" title="Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar 37" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/yamcats-37/" display-uri="yamcats-37" type="local">YaMCaTS 37</fr:link> next week</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>I am traveling to Sheffield on Tuesday, to speak at the <fr:link href="/yamcats-37/" title="Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar 37" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/yamcats-37/" display-uri="yamcats-37" type="local">Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar</fr:link> the following day. I haven’t prepared my talk yet, but I will be speaking about my <fr:link href="/pugh-sterling-2025/" title="When is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone?" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/pugh-sterling-2025/" display-uri="pugh-sterling-2025" type="local">joint work</fr:link> with <fr:link href="/leonipugh/" title="Leoni Pugh" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/leonipugh/" display-uri="leonipugh" type="local">Leoni Pugh</fr:link> on the geometry of partial map classifiers, which <fr:link href="/jms-01A6/" title="Weeknotes 2025-W15 › Two papers to appear in LICS ’25 › With Leoni Pugh: When is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone?" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-01A6/" display-uri="jms-01A6" type="local">I discussed in my previous weeknote</fr:link>. I’ll be returning to Cambridge on Thursday, in time to have a <fr:link href="/jms-00GP/" title="Clare College" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00GP/" display-uri="jms-00GP" type="local">College</fr:link> lunch the following day with <fr:link href="/anilmadhavapeddy/" title="Anil Madhavapeddy" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/anilmadhavapeddy/" display-uri="anilmadhavapeddy" type="local">Anil</fr:link>’s student <fr:link href="/patrickferris/" title="Patrick Ferris" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/patrickferris/" display-uri="patrickferris" type="local">Patrick Ferris</fr:link>, who has been doing <fr:link href="https://patrick.sirref.org/weekly-2025-03-31/" type="external">very interesting things</fr:link> with <fr:link href="/foreign/www.forester-notes.org/index/" title="Forester" uri="https://www.forester-notes.org/index/" display-uri="https://www.forester-notes.org/index/" type="local">Forester</fr:link>.</html:p>
